{"Title":"青菜肉丝平菇汤的做法","Primary":["小白菜150克","猪肉50克","平菇50克"],"Auxiliary":["油20克","盐2克","味精适量","榨菜丝1袋"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.猪瘦肉切丝","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224202025981.jpg","2.加盐、料酒、生姜末腌制","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224212574906.jpg","3.加入一匙油拌匀，腌制15分钟以上","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224214347988.jpg","4.锅中放少许油，将生姜末煸炒出香味","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224215400082.jpg","5.加水烧开","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224216426265.jpg","6.调入适量盐","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224217431377.jpg","7.将腌制好的肉丝慢慢氽入沸腾的水中","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224218730997.jpg","8.水开后改小火，用勺子撇去浮沫","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224219829719.jpg","9.氽入洗净的青菜和平菇","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224221789731.jpg","10.加入适量榨菜丝","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224226669064.jpg","11.加入榨菜丝","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224228597833.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224230088725.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/237/01/1250487/n1250487_142224230499360.jpg","烹饪技巧","青菜比较嫩，所以直接氽入汤中"]}